{"tid":1857651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連臍帶女嬰 寒冬下被棄兒童之家門外","createTime":"2020-02-02T09:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T11:48:23.000Z","uid":48360,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a35e4b6fee1b71a0e072f66fcd2237fcba0df215","tid":1857651,"uid":48360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200202/ZNV43VET2NWSMDDUXISHMZ35XE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200202%2FZNV43VET2NWSMDDUXISHMZ35XE%2F&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9MLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=b249e34b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200202%2FZNV43VET2NWSMDDUXISHMZ35XE%2F&h=5effb288\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200202/ZNV43VET2NWSMDDUXISHMZ35XE/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慈雲山沙田坳道120號播道兒童之家，凌晨5時許，一名女嬰被人棄置在兒童之家門口。有晨運客途經見女嬰大哭，上前查看揭發，通知兒童之家職員及報警，救護員趕至現場，將女嬰送往伊利沙伯醫院檢驗。女嬰當時被一件白色衣服包裹着，放在一個尼龍膠袋內，沒有表面傷痕，仍身纏臍帶，相信剛出生不久。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後發圖呼籲，急欲會晤一名於今日在黃大仙被遺棄女嬰的親人，呼籲女嬰親人或有資料提供的市民，盡快與任何一間警署聯絡，或致電3661 1632或3661 6039與黃大仙警區人員聯絡。"},{"pid":"8de16292e52ccab5f8f17f047dc74e0e4c94d693","tid":1857651,"uid":186844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:37:46.000Z","msg":"中出爽完唔使負責咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96474f0580b3ab1be0b4ca0704d6fb6221d7757b","tid":1857651,"uid":264158,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:39:13.000Z","msg":"屌 以為中國"},{"pid":"44f569e614edb7796ff7506366878af74e2e597c","tid":1857651,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n警方其後發圖<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n發圖 發訊息 發視頻<br />\n蝗語成功入侵了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class